text: # Assuming the 'Duration' column contains strings in the format "Xh Ym" (e.g., "2h 30m")  # Extract the minutes from the 'Duration' column and handle missing values (NaN) final_df['duration_minute'] = final_df['Duration'].str.split(' ').str[1].str.split('m').str[0]  # Replace missing (NaN) values with 0 final_df['duration_minute'] = final_df['duration_minute'].fillna('0')  # Convert the extracted minutes to integers final_df['duration_minute'] = final_df['duration_minute'].astype(int)
